"'''{{lang|ss|Nkulunkulu Mnikati wetibusiso temaSwati}}'''" is the [[national anthem]] of [[Eswatini]]. It is a compromise between Swazi and western styles of music, and was adopted after independence in 1968.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nationalanthems.info/sz.htm |title=Swaziland |work=nationalanthems.info |accessdate=2009-10-04}}</ref> The lyrics were authored by Fanyana Simelane, and the composer of the tune was David Rycroft.

