===Anime===
An anime television series adaptation by [[AXsiZ]] premiered October 7, 2018 on [[Tokyo MX]] and other channels.<ref name="ANN2">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-08-03/ulysses-jeanne-darc-and-the-alchemist-knight-anime-reveals-cast-visual/.135056|title=''Ulysses: Jeanne d'Arc and the Alchemist Knight'' Anime Reveals Cast, Visual|website=Anime News Network|date=August 3, 2018|accessdate=August 3, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2017-10-25/ulysses-jeanne-darc-to-renkin-no-kishi-fantasy-novels-have-anime-in-the-works/.123218|title=''Ulysses: Jeanne d'Arc to Renkin no Kishi'' Fantasy Novels Have Anime in the Works|website=Anime News Network|date=October 25, 2017|accessdate=October 28, 2017}}</ref> The series is directed by Shin Itagaki, with [[Ryunosuke Kingetsu]] handling series composition, Jouji Sawada designing the characters, and [[Taku Iwasaki]] composing the music.<ref name="ANN1">{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-05-05/ulysses-jeanne-darc-to-renkin-no-kishi-anime-reveals-cast-staff-promo-video-october-premiere/.131216|title=''Ulysses: Jeanne d'Arc to Renkin no Kishi'' Anime Reveals Cast, Staff, Promo Video, October Premiere|website=[[Anime News Network]]|date=May 5, 2018|accessdate=May 5, 2018}}</ref> The opening theme is {{Nihongo|"Libération"|リベラシオン}} by [[Mai Fuchigami]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-09-20/ulysses-jeanne-darc-and-the-alchemist-knight-anime-video-previews-mai-fuchigami-song/.137068|title=''Ulysses: Jeanne d'Arc and the Alchemist Knight'' Anime's Video Previews Mai Fuchigami Song|website=Anime News Network|date=September 20, 2018|accessdate=September 20, 2018}}</ref> and the ending theme is {{Nihongo|"Hundred years' melammu"|百年のメラム}} by [[rionos]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-09-10/rionos-performs-ulysses-jeanne-darc-and-the-alchemist-knight-anime-ending-theme/.136572|title=rionos Performs ''Ulysses: Jeanne d'Arc and the Alchemist Knight'' Anime's Ending Theme|website=Anime News Network|date=September 10, 2018|accessdate=September 10, 2018}}</ref> The series is simulcast by [[Crunchyroll]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-07-06/crunchyroll-lists-fall-simulcast-for-ulysses-jeanne-darc-and-the-alchemist-knight-anime/.133929 |title=Crunchyroll Lists Fall Simulcast for ''Ulysses: Jeanne d'Arc and the Alchemist Knight'' Anime |date=July 6, 2018 |website=Anime News Network |accessdate=July 6, 2018}}</ref> with [[Funimation]] streaming the simuldub.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-09-25/funimation-adds-ulysses-goblin-slayer-senran-kagura-radiant-anime-to-fall-season-dub-lineup/.137295|title=Funimation Adds Ulysses, Goblin Slayer, Senran Kagura, Radiant Anime to Fall Season Dub Lineup|website=Anime News Network|date=September 25, 2018|accessdate=September 25, 2018}}</ref> The series will run for 12 episodes.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/daily-briefs/2018-10-01/ulysses-anime-listed-with-12-episodes/.137509|title=Ulysses Anime Listed With 12 Episodes|website=Anime News Network|date=October 1, 2018|accessdate=October 1, 2018}}</ref>. On November 27, due to unrevealed reasons, AXsiZ announces that the episode 9 will be postponed for a week.

